cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with Natural Language Processing (NLP) and relation classification and extraction. The use of neural networks also suggests that it could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper involves analyzing the importance of features, which could place it in cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Finally, the use of an ensemble of neural networks could suggest it belongs to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
